<h1 id="cool-jekyll-blog-theme">Cool Jekyll Blog Theme</h1>

<p>This is a blog theme based on jekyll. You can use on your own blog.
Before you use it, please click a star on <a href="https://github.com/Gaohaoyang/gaohaoyang.github.io/">this
respository</a>. You
will encourage me to do more great things!</p>

